Rules are in place to be broken, and this trend proves it. The rule used to be "combine bright colors with neutral shades". Luckily, there's more room for us to experiment nowadays. Why don't you try putting together an entire outfit in the same shade?

You can execute this trend as safely or experimentally as you wish: go to work in an outfit that's completely olive green or leave your house in red trousers, sweater and shoes. Find a jumpsuit in one solid color or put together an outfit with a bunch of items in the same shade.

Not a fan of an outfit in one color? Complete your look with an accessory in a color that stands out but still perfectly matches your chosen main colour. Use the My Color Passport app to find the perfect accent color for every outfit.

